metadata.name: Indigenous people protesting
metadata.description:
"Wayuu indigenous community held a sit-in symbolizing, for the thousands of deaths of children in La Guajira due to poor nutrition and lack of water."

This photograph was taken on 5 May 2016 in one of the most iconic places in the city of Bogota, the Plaza de Bolivar in the centre of the city. 

Dimensions: 5184px * 3456px
